document_data.name: Al-Anf
document_data.mainbody:
'''Al-Anf''', also called '''The Nose''', was a small easterly island found in the [[Genie's Turban]] archipelago in the [[Corsair Domains]] of [[northwest Zakhara]] around [[1367 DR]].{{AQ-time}}

Al-Anf and [[Al-Oyun]] were collectively referred to as the "Beauty Marks" by local [[Corsair (kit)|corsairs]]. Ever distrustful of strangers, the corsairs would use the term as a form of password to test outsiders.
document_data.Geography: The island was the farthest southeast point of the Genie's Turban. It was a small forested island measuring roughly {{SI|15|mi|k|long=yes}} in diameter.
